Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:28.94,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}北風　吹かれる吐息、願いを込める
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.92,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}僕らと星空…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:35.81,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}きっと、繋ぐ夢…叶う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:38.83,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}僕らと星空…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:46.02,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}きっと、繋ぐ夢…叶う。
