Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:33.37,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢想隨著北風  飽含著願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:36.47,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}向著我們的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.76,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}由大地之光照亮
